ActIndian Band Election Regulations
SubjectFisher River First Nation - Indian Band Election Regulations
PrecisOrder acknowledging receipt of the report of the Minister of Indigenous Services, indicating that there was a violation of the INDIAN BAND ELECTION REGULATIONS that may have affected the results of the August 23, 2017 election of the council of the FISHER RIVER FIRST NATION, located in Manitoba.
